text: Khaki is a color, a yellowish light shade of brown. == Tones of khaki == === Light Khaki === * A light, yellowish shade of khaki. === Dark Khaki=== * Dark Khaki is a darker shade of khaki. === Khaki Green === * Khaki green is a shade of khaki. == Color codes == * In hex:#C3B091 == Related articles == * Yellow * Brown * Orange
title: Khaki
